	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">为全面贯彻落实党的十九大精神，进一步加强机关思想政治建设和作风建设，全面提高机关工作人员的综合素质，培养造就一支适应新形势、新任务，政治素质过硬、理论水平深厚、业务技能精湛的经济工作队伍，牢固树立并贯彻落实新发展理念，鼓足干劲创造新业绩，经信委狠抓业务学习和内部挖潜，提出创建学习型机关，制定如下实施意见：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">一、指导思想</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">本着</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">干什么学什么，主抓什么精什么，参与什么懂什么，缺什么补什么</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的原则，集中集体智慧，既做到学习内容的全面性，又兼顾不同岗位不同人员的具体情况，精心布局，系统筹划，从政治理论、经济常识、行业技术、法律法规等方面详细制定学<SPAN style="COLOR: black">习计划。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">大力营造重视学习、崇尚学习、坚持学习的浓厚氛围，牢固确立全员学习、终身学习的理念，树立科学的学习观，创建具有较强的学习力、文化力、创新力、领导力的学习型机关，全力提高全委基层党组织和党员干部的工作水平和执政能力，使全委的创造力、凝聚力、战斗力不断增强。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">二、学习内容</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（一）政治理论。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">认真学习马列主义、毛泽东思想，邓小平理论、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">三个代表</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">重要思想以及科学发展观；党的基本理论、基本路线、基本纲领、党的十九大精神，党和国家的路线、方针、政策，党在改革开放实践中形成的最新理论创新成果和中央、省、市一系列重要会议精神。要坚持理论联系实际，在学习的系统性和深度上下功夫，在武装头脑、指导实践、推动工作上出成效。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（二）经济知识。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">学习社会主义市场经济知识、现代金融知识、现代管理知识、市重点行业技术理论等知识。通过学习，使全体人员进一步增强以经济建设为中心的意识，不断提高为经济建设服务的能力和水平。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（三）法律法规。学习社会主义法制理论、法律法规以及中央、省党委关于党风和廉政建设的一系列规定。通过学习，使全体党员了解和掌握与工作相关的法律、法规和条例，提高依法决策、依法行政、依法管理的水平和能力。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（四）科技知识。及时了解和掌握最新的科技发展动态，认真学习新能源、新材料、人工智能等前沿科技动态，光电显示、小核酸等昆山特色产业和机器人及智能装备、半导体等昆山重点发展产业相关技术知识。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（五）文化知识。学习优秀传统文化、历史和社会知识。通过学习，不断丰富党员干部的文化历史和社会知识，提高素质，陶冶情操。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（六）业务知识。根据本部门、本岗位的工作要求和特点，认真学习、专业知识和技术，开展专业知识培训，促进每个党员，干一行，学一行，钻一行，不断提高工作水平和工作能力。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">三、学习形式</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（一）建立经信学堂</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">、邀请北京大学、南京大学等知名高校经济专家，以及市委党校的讲师团或专家学者，为委机关全体人员解析宏观经济形势，解读宏观经济政策、产业发展趋势及前沿技术动态。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">、开展</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">每月一课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">，委领导</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">围绕当前经济社会发展中的重大问题轮流作专题演讲或报告。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（二）启动交流论坛</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">、启动</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">科长讲坛</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">每月排出一位轮值科长，利用半天时间举办讲坛活动。轮值科长结合工作职责，自定主题，以</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>PPT</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">讲座形式交流工作经验、分享前沿知识。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、启动</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">微信论坛</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">每周安排一位轮值人员（副科长、科员），负责发布交流主题，整理交流讨论内容。每周一由轮值人员发布本周活动主题，周五利用经信委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>QQ</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">群或微信群安排一小时交流时间。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、启动</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">外脑论坛</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。每季度邀请市委组织部（人才办）、台办、转型办、企业发展服务中心、发改委（金融办）、科技局、财政局、人社局、商务局、环保局、安监局、市场监管局、统计局、海关、国税局、地税局等部门讲授部门工作内容，交流经济工作管理经验。邀请区镇分管领导讲授基层服务企业经验措施，交流工作心得。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（三）开展读书比赛</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">坚持个人学习为主，根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">支部组织生活学习计划、委领导推荐书目等，结合重大理论问题和现实问题，自行排定学习计划，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">开展读书比赛，每月每人读一本好书、做一份笔记、写一篇心得，月月打擂台、月月评优秀。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（四）开展调研活动</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据委年度工作重点，主要领导带头，分管领导、科长结合工作职责制定重大课题调研计划。分管领导每年至少完成一篇调研材料，科长至少完成两篇调研材料。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">（五）编写场景式服务清单</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据经信委工作职责，梳理出科室工作的法律法规和扶持政策，结合工作流程，编写场景式服务清单，形成工作手册，通过微信公众号发放给区镇、企业，优化办事流程、提高办事效率。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">四、总体要求</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">1．加强领导，明确责任。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">委主要领导作为第一责任人，分管领导要及时督促各科室制定切实可行的学习计划，明确阶段性学习目标和内容，扎实开展各项学习活动。各机关支部、团委、工会要结合创建学习型机关活动，统筹制订学习计划，妥善安排好学习活动，通过学习活动，扎实推进机关作风和效能建设。办公室作为学习型机关的牵头科室，要做好协调推进统筹工作，督促各项学习任务落到实处，并建立相应的学习台帐。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">2．狠抓落实、注重实效。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">要坚持学习工作化、工作学习化，妥善处理和解决工作与学习的矛盾，做到</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">两不误、两促进</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">，要积极探索和实践创建活动的好载体、好方法，努力引导干部职工学以致用，把理论学习和本部门、本岗位实际工作有机结合起来，着力开创经济工作的新局面。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">3．紧密配合、营造氛围。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">各部门要充分利用各种宣传阵地大力宣传建设学习型机关的目的、意义，以及建设活动中的好典型、好经验、好做法。委工会、团委、妇委会要充分发挥自身的优势，配合党组织开展各项主题学习教育活动，将学习型党组织创建活动不断引向深入。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">昆山市经济和信息化委员会</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">19</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
